Aim_vnv_aztec Remade from the original map:
rs_aztec_v2 Also goes by the name of 'aim_aztec' or 'rs_aztec' About: I remade this from scratch. Didn't take long as the original map was pretty basic, but still fun gameplay wise. I pretty much brought this map back to life for my clan. After using the whole aztec style, I realized that I've always loved de_aztec, and aztec style. Hoping to go further with aztec style maps. Features: * 3D Skybox * Rain * Blended Textures Next Steps: Next step is to hopefully continue with this aztec style, and make some more maps. Also to make some more small maps that are just made for fun. And of course, kudos to VNVNation for the original map + layout. :D
